<p>The difference is not luck. It is SEO.</p>
<p>This auto repair shop SEO guide covers every step you need to rank on Google Maps and organic search. We publish 3,500+ blog posts across 70+ industries, and local service businesses like auto repair shops are among the fastest to see results.</p>
<p>Here is what you will learn:</p>
<ul>
