<p>Upload at least 25 photos. Include your shop exterior (helps customers find you), service bays, your team, completed repair work, and your waiting area. Update photos monthly.</p>
<p>Our <a href="/blog/gbp-photos-guide/">GBP photos guide</a> covers the exact types and sizes Google prioritizes. Shops that upload new photos weekly get significantly more engagement.</p>
<h3>Post Regular Updates</h3>
<p>Google rewards active profiles. Post at least once per week with seasonal tips, special offers, or service highlights. GBP posts expire after 7 days, so consistency matters.</p>
