<h3>Realistic Timeline for Results</h3>
<p>SEO is not instant. Set expectations based on reality:</p>
<p><strong>Month 1 to 2:</strong> Foundation work. GBP optimized, website updated, citations submitted, first blog posts published. Minimal ranking changes during this phase.</p>
<p><strong>Month 3 to 4:</strong> Early traction. Keyword positions begin moving. GBP impressions increase. Reviews start growing if you follow the system.</p>
